snippet.title: Mark 1333
snippet.description:
8th June 2019

News and fun clips from around the world. Please keep any comments civil, sensible and in English or they may be removed. 

Disclaimer: No copyright infringement is intended, news clips are of interest and short where possible and/or edited and this channel is not monetised by me, but adverts may appear by any claimants. 

If you would also like to see a complete list in one page, see the following link here:
https://justpaste.it/1lrf7


For new original content, see my other channel Know How Briton, here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCn7ia6V-biaDGA3m6qS9Qhw
